### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5244
@token = YOUR_FIREBASE_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### AUTH APIs
### ============================================

### Get Profile (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### USER APIs
### ============================================

### Get My Info (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get User By ID (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/ei38SSMJQmXyMUOFyRn3EtNLvtz1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Users (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create User (không cần token - dùng cho register)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "ei38SSMJQmXyMUOFyRn3EtNLvtz1",
  "firstName": "Đại",
  "lastName": "Nguyễn",
  "email": "dai@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "dateOfBirth": "2000-01-01",
  "bio": "Hello world"
}

### Update My Info (cần token)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Đại Updated",
  "lastName": "Nguyễn",
  "bio": "Updated bio"
}

### Delete My Account (cần token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### FEED APIs
### ============================================

### Create Feed (cần token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/feed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": [
    {
      "text": "Hello world from API test",
      "media": []
    }
  ]
}

### Get Feed By ID (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/feed/FEED_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get My Feeds (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/feed/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### FRIEND APIs
### ============================================

### Get My Friends (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/friends
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Received Friend Requests (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/friends/requests/received
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Sent Friend Requests (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/friends/requests/sent
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Blocked Users (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/friends/blocked
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Relationship Status (cần token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/friends/status/TARGET_USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Send Friend Request (cần token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/friends/requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "TARGET_USER_ID"
}

### Accept/Reject Friend Request (cần token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/friends/requests/FRIENDSHIP_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "accept"
}

### Cancel Friend Request (cần token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/friends/requests/FRIENDSHIP_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Unfriend (cần token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/friends/TARGET_USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Block User (cần token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/friends/block/TARGET_USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Unblock User (cần token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/friends/block/TARGET_USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### OTP APIs (không cần token)
### ============================================

### Generate OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/otp/generate?email=test@gmail.com

### Verify OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/otp/verify?email=test@gmail.com&otp=123456
